typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		{$dtid} as string,
		{$timestamp} as string,
		SequentialNumber as string,
		EMT as string,
		CreateTime as string,
		Status as string,
		ErrorCode as string,
		TotalNum as string,
		Category as string,
		EventTime as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false) ~> source1
source1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	entity: '',
	format: 'cdm',
	corpusPath: 'jabilcdm',
	folderPath: '',
	fileSystem: '',
	columnDelimiter: ',',
	columnNamesAsHeader: false,
	corpusStore: 'adlsgen2',
	adlsgen2_fileSystem: 'cdm',
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1
